    "description": "游戏特色：<br><br>恐怖氛围营造：<br>游戏通过精致的场景设计、逼真的音效和光影效果，营造出紧张刺激的恐怖氛围。荒废的医学院大楼、阴森的走廊、血迹斑斑的实验室……每一处都充满了危险和未知。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/0d984c28ecc4a09c4e0b7f9d91a338ec.poster.avif?t=1723591815\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/0d984c28ecc4a09c4e0b7f9d91a338ec.webm?t=1723591815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/0d984c28ecc4a09c4e0b7f9d91a338ec.mp4?t=1723591815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>多样化的敌人设计：<br>游戏中的敌人包括各种恐怖生物、幽灵和变异体。它们拥有不同的攻击方式和能力，玩家需要运用智慧和勇气来应对它们的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/ffc3a104471e38da8a86881f1a7daa91.poster.avif?t=1723591815\" width=480 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/ffc3a104471e38da8a86881f1a7daa91.webm?t=1723591815\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346390/extras/ffc3a104471e38da8a86881f1a7daa91.mp4?t=1723591815\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>动作射击机制：<br>游戏采用流畅的动作射击机制，玩家可以使用多种武器和道具来消灭敌人。同时，游戏还融入了闪避、躲避和反击等动作元素，让战斗更加刺激和紧张。<br><br>模拟与日常：<br>玩家将扮演一位在荒废医学院中看守的勇敢看门人，不仅要面对各种恐怖生物的威胁，还要保护自己的小黑猫，并揭开医学院背后的恐怖秘密。",
